<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine - Model Years Late 1997 to 2003 - Turbocharger - Inspection - Check
        Axial End Play
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc graphiccount="1">
        <title>Check Axial End Play</title>
        <figure figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figeg2/eg2491.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Checking Axial End Play</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Dial Indicator</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Turbine Housing</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">With the turbocharger in a stable position, place the tip of a dial indicator inline with
                the end of the turbine shaft. Reset the dial indicator to zero.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Move the shaft back and forth by hand and record the readings. If the readings exceed
                specifications, the turbocharger must be replaced.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
